Oracle-Identity Manager
Job Location:Hyderabad
Job Number:J27629
Schedule: Full-time
• Experienced in identity and access management Well versed with usage of the I&AM; product and domains Technical Design, Build, Configuration, Customization and Testing of I&AM; solutions Design and Development of security for applications using LDAP, PKI, SSSL, JNDI, RSA BSAFE would provide an ideal background. • Participation in conceptual and technical design of Java/J2EE solutions and I&AM; solutions 2 years of strong Java/J2EE design, development, testing and application support experience ; Identity and Access Management solutions deployment, configuration, customization and support. • This should include integration with LDAP, deployment of web agents for access control, configuration of authorization models, single sign-on configurations, build of approval and provisioning workflows, deployment of provisioning adapters, SSL Configuration, configuration of user management, self-service, password resets, forgot password functionality
Graduation in any discipline
